ComicInfo.Title: Chapter Three: Past Mistakes
ComicInfo.Summary: Big things happen! Featuring the fan-favorite new character “Dee” Donovan! That’s her on the cover! I think I have a thing for powerful women. It has a lot to do with stuff that happened to me as a child. I don’t really want to get into it here!!
